text.section:
The student member shall:
Be an 11th or 12th grade student in the St. Mary's County Public School System;
Serve for 1 year;
Be a nonvoting member; and
Advise the county board on the thoughts and feelings of the students.

section.section:
The State Board may remove a member of the county board for:
Immorality;
Misconduct in office;
Incompetence; or
Willful neglect of duty.
